OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1780481194
OL,3,CMan arrested after car 'driven
OL,4,Crepeatedly' at pedestrian
OL,6,FA man has been arrested as part of an
OL,7,Fattempted murder investigation in
OL,8,FNorthumberland.
OL,10,FPolice say a black Audi A3 was
OL,11,Freported to have been driven
OL,12,F"repeatedly" at a pedestrian in
OL,13,FAlnwick before striking them and
OL,14,Fleaving the scene.
OL,16,FIt happened at about 6.40pm on Friday
OL,17,F(29 May) on St Thomas' Crescent, at
OL,18,Fthe junction with Sycamore Avenue.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
