OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1780481194
OL,3,CMan arrested after car 'driven
OL,4,Crepeatedly' at pedestrian
OL,6,FAt about 6.40pm yesterday (May 29),
OL,7,Fpolice responded to a report of a
OL,8,Fserious assault on St Thomas' Crescent
OL,9,Fat the junction with Sycamore Avenue
OL,10,Fin Alnwick.
OL,12,FThe pedestrian, a man aged in his
OL,13,F30's, was taken to hospital for
OL,14,Ftreatment of serious leg injuries.
OL,16,FA 21-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,17,Fsuspicion of attempted murder.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1780481194
OL,3,CMan arrested after car 'driven
OL,4,Crepeatedly' at pedestrian
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Adele Catlow, of
OL,7,FNorthumbria Police, said: "This has
OL,8,Fclearly been a very serious incident
OL,9,Fwhich has resulted in a man sustaining
OL,10,Fsignificant injuries.
OL,12,F"The investigation is at an early
OL,13,Fstage, but we do believe that those
OL,14,Finvolved are known to each other.
OL,16,F"We have made an arrest, and our
OL,17,Fofficers will continue to conduct
OL,18,Fenquiries in the area and offer
OL,19,Freassurance to the public.
OL,26,@oD@[OUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1780481194
OL,3,CMan arrested after car 'driven
OL,4,Crepeatedly' at pedestrian
OL,6,F"We are keen to speak with anyone who
OL,7,Fmay have witnessed the incident or was
OL,8,Ftravelling in the area at the time.
OL,10,F"Please come forward ` the information
OL,11,Fyou are able to provide might just
OL,12,Fprove crucial in helping to establish
OL,13,Fthe circumstances behind this report."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@fO]
