OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1780481194
OL,3,CMan arrested after car 'driven
OL,4,Crepeatedly' at pedestrian
OL,6,FAnyone with information that could
OL,7,Fhelp with the investigation, in
OL,8,Fparticular witnesses who may have CCTV
OL,9,For dashcam footage, should get in
OL,10,Ftouch by sending a direct message on
OL,11,Fsocial media to Northumbria Police, or
OL,12,Fby using the live chat function or
OL,13,Freport forms on the force's website.
OL,14,FFor those unable to get in touch in
OL,15,Fthose ways, call 101.
OL,17,FThe reference number is NP-20260529-
OL,18,F0981.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/6
